article.description: — Tylor Perry scored 19 points to lead North Texas over Western Kentucky 67-33 on Saturday.
article.headline: Perry lifts North Texas over Western Kentucky 67-33
article.linkText: Perry lifts North Texas over Western Kentucky 67-33
article.story:
DENTON, Texas -- — Tylor Perry scored 19 points to lead North Texas over Western Kentucky 67-33 on Saturday.

Perry shot 6 for 14 from the floor (4 for 11 from 3-point range) and 3 of 3 from the free-throw line for the Mean Green (25-6, 16-4 Conference USA). Aaron Scott totaled 11 points, seven rebounds and three steals.

Jamarion Sharp led the Hilltoppers (16-15, 8-12) with eight points, 11 rebounds and three steals. Jordan Rawls added seven points.

------
